-   <span data-ttu-id="ec81a-414">es-ES.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ec81a-414">es-ES.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ec81a-415">Spagnolo (Spagna)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ec81a-415">Spanish (Spain)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="ec81a-416">fr-FR.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ec81a-416">fr-FR.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ec81a-417">Francese (Francia)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ec81a-417">French (France)</span></span>  
  
